'From Squeak3.6alpha of ''17 March 2003'' [latest update: #5325] on 4 July 2003 at 12:25:06 pm'!"Change Set:		OptionalWarningForMacOSFileNameLength-dgdDate:			4 July 2003Author:			Diego Gomez Deck <DiegoGomezDeck@ConsultAr.com>- Make optional the warning about the Mac OS file name lenght.- See the new Preferences option named warningForMacOSFileNameLength in fileout category"Preferences	addPreference: #warningForMacOSFileNameLength	category: #fileout	default: false	balloonHelp: 'If true, a check for Mac OS file name length is performed.'.!